creator: dealsplant
descriptionHtml:
The dealsplant Online Shopping App brings you, original products, at lowest prices compared to any other shopping sites in India. Shop on the dealsplant App for the latest electronics, Mobile phones & Accessories – Redmi 5 Pro, Apple iPhone Xs, Xs Max, XR, Samsung S9, OnePlus 6 & more, accessories - memory cards, earphones, chargers, power banks. Shop for unique products, Innovative Electronics, Refurbished mobiles, imported products, hard to get Electronics gadgets / connectors / cables, Car Accessories, LED Lighting, Rechargeable Batteries, Solar Products, CCTV cameras, Bags, Beauty Products, Home made products and many more. We are growing our catalogs constantly. With Bulk buying options, Corporate Gifts and Gift Cards You can delight your Employees or Clients. You may suggest products, ask for any unavailable / rare products / accessories - Any brand any model, We strive hard to procure and list for you. Special discounts for bulk buying / business customers. Download the dealsplant Shopping App for free, from Google Play Store & enjoy online shopping like never before.

Great Shopping Experience:
The free online shopping app from dealsplant assures you of a great shopping experience with a lighter app, faster load time & wide selection across categories. You can browse and search for your desired products by product name, category or brands. Enjoy the rich catalog images - you can view the product from multiple angles, with options to zoom.
With dealsplant, you are guaranteed very good customer support, faster delivery, easy returns, and convenient payment options

Enjoy Safe and Secure Shopping:
Shop using paytm, UPI, Google Pay, Credit/Debit Card, EMI or Net Banking knowing that all transactions are securely processed. No need to worry about your personal or account details getting leaked, as dealsplant uses CC avenue payment gateway which is 100% Secured and industry leader in payments.


Track your Orders:
Shopping on the dealsplant app offers you updates on the status of your orders.

Shopping is Fun on the dealsplant App:
Get deals & discounts only on the app. App-only offers and discounts posted frequently. Get Special Free gifts only on the App.

Permissions:
In order to offer you the best experience and operate properly, the dealsplant Shopping App needs access to the following services:
* Operating System Requirements: Requires Android OS 2.3 or higher.
* Account: Account permissions are needed for integration with Facebook & other social media network you have connected to your device to allow you to share products with family & friends.

Enjoy the app! Happy Shopping!
